  <name>Renedown</name>
  <summary>Cross-platform Markdown viewer/editor built with Repose</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Renedown is a cross-platform Markdown viewer and editor built as a
      reference example for the Repose GUI framework. It demonstrates how to
      build a full-featured application with:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Rich Markdown rendering (GFM, tables, footnotes, task lists, math)</li>
      <li>Syntax-highlighted code blocks via syntect</li>
      <li>LaTeX math rendering</li>
      <li>Responsive two-pane / single-pane layout</li>
      <li>Native file open/save dialogs</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support (Linux, macOS, Windows, Web, Android)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <developer_name>MLM Games</developer_name>
